title: Ep. 60: Comic-Con Trailers, 'The Night Of,' and 'Stranger Things'
description:
The Ringer's Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald discuss the trailers of 'Justice League,' 'Dr. Strange,'  and 'Wonder Woman.' Then, they break down episode three of 'The Night Of' (30:00) and episodes three through five of 'Stranger Things' (39:00).
